data.description:
All diamonds need to be polished!  With this home's location and features a little shine will go a long way! The fenced yard has room for a garden, play area and has flower beds as well.  The HUGE family room has a fireplace and great views of almost the entire backyard and walks out to the patio. Original hardwood floors adorn the bedrooms and living room.  The lower level has a media/ gaming/ 2nd family room with a fireplace.  The office could be a non-conforming bedroom.  Oh, and don't miss the sauna. 

Great location!  Easy access to highways, shopping, parks and all that Burnsville has to offer. Don't miss this GEM!
